{"tid":360884,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"自high東歐遊記分享","createTime":"2017-08-15T16:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T18:07:01.000Z","uid":53780,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"343590994699bbd04413f4c1b684edad1b1ed42d","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"今次應該係我第二次踏足歐洲既土地<br />\n上一次去歐洲已經係一年前exchange 既時候<br />\n由於上次主要集中去北歐同中南歐<br />\n今次既旅程就會圍繞係東歐<br />\n<br />\n其實我今年就岩岩fresh grad<br />\n諗到人生仲有四十年人要做奴工<br />\n所以決定係正式番工前去番個旅行先<br />\n雖然眼見好多fd已經收哂offer 番緊工<br />\n都不其然地感到壓力<br />\n但係最後都係決定玩完先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左今次呢個grad trip <br />\n特登番左2個月full time工儲錢<br />\n<br />\n最後，其實呢個遊記唔知會唔會有人睇，無就當俾自己拎黎自high啦"},{"pid":"d2c22354bd675a58bd69f48c089489c35aa5409e","tid":360884,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8cc8e8f0ce40a041520cc62b6391f21cfa1de4","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"首先，講下我個行程先<br />\n16/8 香港&gt;莫斯科（dme )<br />\n16-19/8 莫斯科<br />\n20-23/8 基輔+Chernobyl<br />\n23-28/8 Budapest <br />\n28-31/8 stockholm <br />\n<br />\n今次搭既航空係Qatar airline <br />\n買到平機票，來回歐洲先3810hkd 抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0dw96cga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0dw96cga&h=e79bdd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛凌晨一點，差唔多上機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r6bpomyc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr6bpomyc&h=fd45d9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港飛多哈<br />\n再褔多哈飛到莫斯科<br />\n<br />\n希望陣間唔好有細路嘈住我訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc79819eb29f625f4b5084210950bdc52d54aa97","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"上機喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d05zr4we\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd05zr4we&h=8638d2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個位雖然有d窄<br />\n但係個電視都OK大<br />\n電影仲有中文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v82ma9wz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv82ma9wz&h=93b868a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有氈 牙刷 眼罩 耳塞<br />\n<br />\n仲有支唔知咩黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/ujyf60rw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fujyf60rw&d=d23azUcGDkfI%2FZaGypc7aQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fe97788b\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/ujyf60rw</a>"},{"pid":"4f03e5060b631b7b38b0fdfeb493e4307e4c2e25","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次搭飛機係呢個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒下粒制個窗會逐漸變黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5dl6vf3i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5dl6vf3i&h=7d981a61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31af444bcffffb5bfd3a909d0862b08da68e8414","tid":360884,"uid":122285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩7月去完北歐 好想再去"},{"pid":"ff1e041a82dd86eecd18b47a580719ca8bd1ad13","tid":360884,"uid":14282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"去moscow點解唔揾直航 又快d又平d"},{"pid":"cb860ab7322462cdb46ea70ec0f571111178013b","tid":360884,"uid":99621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"巴打23號去bp，我23bp走🤦🏼&zwj;♂️🤦🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"3be38ec9c7fa757cce20619a7c1d8b804cdcb2a6","tid":360884,"uid":40042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T20:15:10.000Z","msg":"暑假檔期搵到$38xx機票 勁"},{"pid":"04bdb0b587fb5e2e3ef1122b3d0774de47d44049","tid":360884,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次搭飛機係呢個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒下粒制個窗會逐漸變黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5dl6vf3i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5dl6vf3i&h=7d981a61&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n787<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4bbb3b99efdf8f11bca99cfc0b10349ea2ff54","tid":360884,"uid":1841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暑假檔期搵到$38xx機票 勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEithad大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73037a111c7a0989df05c6fbc8836e4361be03bb","tid":360884,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:33:42.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓豬有冇乖乖跟我幫你plan個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae6f1e3e9eac12807cd1910479a500f0d5a207f","tid":360884,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde1caca329c801d7c00197afa8a1cf0d1413b77","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩7月去完北歐 好想再去</blockquote><br />\n去左咩國家？"},{"pid":"3320ee62ee37f76f68826b729994392b5d293930","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去moscow點解唔揾直航 又快d又平d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我搵過直飛都幾貴"},{"pid":"fb6879a7b87771cdf9079cdb63f6f995200b1866","tid":360884,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c5e3d1076541d199a9615e41d7ad001343ef0b","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:06:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭完8個鐘機，終於到多哈<br />\n個機場好大好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可惜我只係transfer <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wrp832e1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwrp832e1&h=beb4e5ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c74qhz01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc74qhz01&h=5f8e6039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中東佬係咪太有錢，擺一堆apple 電腦係機場俾人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1tj50ez2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1tj50ez2&h=ffda1614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBtw 點解佢地唔洗訓教，呢邊5：05am , 所有商鋪都已經開哂定唔知係24hr營業"},{"pid":"f9341604896efcce1e3615c442a7fbbbe5ba38f9","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇樓豬有冇乖乖跟我幫你plan個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盡量跟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇我起唔起到身"},{"pid":"63ab645846cbd80d39bf0c9fb5dd769c5a45dc49","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"終於到左俄羅斯<br />\n去到border 等左我成半粒鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2myi95nu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2myi95nu&h=20f25ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文字都唔多隻<br />\n好撚嬲係前面果班唔知係中東人定南亞人係咁撚插隊<br />\n同佢講排隊又唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我最後要搵手欄住佢地<br />\n跟住大聲講 stop! I am first <br />\n之後頭也不回上左前<br />\n<br />\n終於出機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4tql6vrg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4tql6vrg&h=c0407f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/u5tnlobd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu5tnlobd&d=d23azUcGDkfI%2FZaGypc7aQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=db7b1875\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/u5tnlobd</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯機場都真係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵哂全個機場先得幾部ATM，仲要得一部係銀聯<br />\nBtw aeroexpress 離佢機場9丈遠，而且好荒蕪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vs069t1l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvs069t1l&h=d265482e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd5bb5f130da284f905e5aa2835f5eea0bae0cdc","tid":360884,"uid":137134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於到左俄羅斯<br />\n去到border 等左我成半粒鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2myi95nu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2myi95nu&h=20f25ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文字都唔多隻<br />\n好撚嬲係前面果班唔知係中東人定<span style=\"color: red;\">南亞人</span>係咁撚插隊<br />\n同佢講排隊又唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我最後要搵手欄住佢地<br />\n跟住大聲講 stop! I am first <br />\n之後頭也不回上左前<br />\n<br />\n終於出機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4tql6vrg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4tql6vrg&h=c0407f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/u5tnlobd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu5tnlobd&d=d23azUcGDkfI%2FZaGypc7aQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=db7b1875\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/u5tnlobd</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯機場都真係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵哂全個機場先得幾部ATM，仲要得一部係銀聯<br />\nBtw aeroexpress 離佢機場9丈遠，而且好荒蕪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vs069t1l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvs069t1l&h=d265482e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最撚憎南亞狗 去邊都撞到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28df844b45516be5d9b4008cc1b8af5451a75abd","tid":360884,"uid":60550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"上年我歐洲exchange 主要玩中歐東歐西歐 都去左chernobyl<br />\n今年grad trip去左巴爾幹<br />\n好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想再去"},{"pid":"7efa0cb7e80a1059f5c451df5336188b0509d44c","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:05:34.000Z","msg":"今日第一日黎到加試搭左十幾個鐘飛機<br />\n所以決定坐定定睇馬戲團，費事咁快玩殘自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我之後搵過資料，莫斯科有2個出名既馬戲團<br />\n<br />\n第一個係（俄羅斯莫斯科國家大馬戲團 Bolshoi Circus ）<br />\n但係而家好似維修緊唔開<br />\n<br />\n第二間就係我去果間（尼庫林馬戲團Nikulin Circus）<br />\n<br />\n上網check過每日既1900都會有一場演出<br />\n咁我去到酒店放低行李就狗衝去，果陣係1700，希望趕到<br />\n<br />\n中途搭metro 發現左一樣野<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/slde692n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fslde692n&h=29a70156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解metro條條電梯都咁長，等足兩三分鐘先到地面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n趕時間真係屌出黎"},{"pid":"2decf3aeedeffbf02660346374cf7066c1bdd3dc","tid":360884,"uid":122285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩7月去完北歐 好想再去</blockquote><br />\n去左咩國家？</blockquote><br />\n丹麥 瑞典 芬蘭"},{"pid":"4300522881aaa4605480f2fc90c1070189bfd18d","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:32:44.000Z","msg":"接近1800終於到遲<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r5uktvnh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr5uktvnh&h=f60b96eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尼庫林馬戲團<br />\n<br />\n今日劇目 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fytsqeuz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffytsqeuz&h=eedd9e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好可惜黎緊三日都賣哂<br />\n正當我想走果陣，有個呀叔行埋黎話有飛問我買唔買<br />\n屌佢老味<br />\n原來係黃牛撚買撚哂d飛<br />\n2500ruble 佢開3000<br />\n<br />\n咁我都去到，無理由空手而回<br />\n屌那媽，見佢係靚位就買啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1jnpzxv4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1jnpzxv4&h=4584b365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d00f0ab4fba8fd8f870c8f923bf73f584c31ee2","tid":360884,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T20:46:45.000Z","msg":"1900夠時間就入去啦<br />\n佢會早d放你入去安檢同買野食果d<br />\n一入到去，見到有一排攤位，每個位有一d扮到好靚既動物<br />\n<br />\n由於樓豬係一個極鍾意多毛大狗既人<br />\n咁緊係想行埋去同佢地玩加影相啦<br />\n點知場館d人話影相要俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n采你都傻，好彩偷影到一張佢先話no photo <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bamy6uft\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbamy6uft&h=be3b1735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇 終於入去會場喇<br />\n當初諗住起碼都紅館咁大啦，點知入到去見到係好似修頓場咁上下大，有少少失望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vcxb0d63\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F